# Reference only — public hostnames for the prod deployment.
#
# These are configured in:
#   - traefik/dynamic/routes.yaml   (router Host rules)
#   - compose.prod.yaml             (KC_HOSTNAME)
#   - each app's .env               (AUTH_URL / issuer URLs)
#
# Keep them in sync if you change the domain.
#
#   auth.patocapital.com     -> Keycloak
#   tenants.patocapital.com  -> tenancy-portal
#   apps.patocapital.com     -> fineract-ui (banking)
#
# Per-service settings live in <service>/.env (see <service>/.env.example).
